-06-19T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"879cf3c734d2a0326123463f15bc35c474206a66","tid":1243275,"uid":260806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"請留意股壇長毛嘅 Webb-site 裏面有呢篇<br />\nHong Kong's not-so-free economy (4 February 2018)<br />\n<a href=\"https://webb-site.com/articles/notsofree.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebb-site.com%2Farticles%2Fnotsofree.asp&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2B6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=d47d87ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webb-site.com/articles/notsofree.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n裏面有一句：<br />\n<strong>There is <span style=\"color: red;\">no class action system</span> in HK</strong> to provide access to justice in cases involving a dispersed group of victims. In 2012 after 3 years of study and consultation, the Law Reform Commission recommended the introduction of a limited system for consumer actions relating to goods and services (but not investments). The Government deferred this by forming another committee to study the proposals which, over 5 years later, has yet to report back.<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅集體訴訟制度遙遙無期。<br />\n<br />\n小弟大概常識咁嘅水準，刑事我唔識，亦暫時冇 idea。<br />\n<br />\n民事索償方面，讀過 Tort Law 嘅朋友應該知道「公衆妨擾」(Public Nuisance)，受害人會構成一個 Class，其中任何一個受害人都可以入稟，唔需要搵全部人一齊去。<br />\n<br />\n但警察會話基於佢哋係執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n如果有機會入，呢種源源不絕嘅財路（贏到之後會有一堆人來搵佢一樣幫手索償），律師一定好願意做。"},{"pid":"c58e2e7e33f0fc35cfc1140537c9d50bd9748b42","tid":1243275,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55f58b66b2b2d0e70c376b22ba401c2cc5a3ede0","tid":1243275,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:47:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d92bb78937e604885d9c88eef2afcd6ddf619945","tid":1243275,"uid":258956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:48:14.000Z","msg":"自己一個都可以告，1st defendant: Members of Hong Kong Police Force of unknown identities. 2nd defendant: secretary for justice on behalf of Commission of Police.<br />\n<br />\n證明兩樣嘢：1.警方當日在現場（中信）使用不當武力，2.你因為警方不當武力而受傷（最好當日有睇醫生，有證明）"},{"pid":"8c63908e36fe5b8715f31f9f5cc1f11f29d0e23d","tid":1243275,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92bb78937e604885d9c88eef2afcd6ddf619945","tid":1243275,"uid":258956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:48:14.000Z","msg":"自己一個都可以告，1st defendant: Members of Hong Kong Police Force of unknown identities. 2nd defendant: secretary for justice on behalf of Commission of Police.<br />\n<br />\n證明兩樣嘢：1.警方當日在現場（中信）使用不當武力，2.你因為警方不當武力而受傷（最好當日有睇醫生，有證明）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"係民事索償，personal injury"},{"pid":"f93e61f64f7aeaf3bbd84e0671c33e685e0699e3","tid":1243275,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:52:52.000Z","msg":"香港沒有集體訴訟司法制度，但能透過代表性訴訟，把有共同訴求或類同的訴訟人個案，向法院提出「代表性訴訟」<br />\n<br />\n雷曼事件苦主曾經使用「代表性訴訟」去告銀行"},{"pid":"de397b919412228bf3a5566acf8cb2716a6f297e","tid":1243275,"uid":264994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"220e7345659619b1407fd08e2f12ded1125240ca","tid":1243275,"uid":72645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e684899b834d080294ae443156fda0c7d8a995c4","tid":1243275,"uid":142499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67af215e6668f980925ff544c46fe27bbaded862","tid":1243275,"uid":88503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f00a32abf9149c0028eb6ab2f0c36b7a57c83c31","tid":1243275,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"推，集思廣益"},{"pid":"a914bdea40848db0ff3844de6b34830a2c6fd9bf","tid":1243275,"uid":70619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}